    <item>
      <title>拜登希望黑人、拉丁裔领导人平息党内叛乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/biden-looks-to-black-latino-leaders-to-put-down-party-uprising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登正在向黑人、西班牙裔和进步派领袖寻求帮助，以遏制党内因其是否适合担任公职而引发的抗议，这对于这位在这些群体选民中的地位已经下降的总统来说是一条意想不到的生命线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/biden-looks-to-black-latino-leaders-to-put-down-party-uprising</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对欧盟贸易壁垒展开反击调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/china-launches-tit-for-tat-investigation-into-eu-trade-barriers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正在调查欧盟针对世界第二大经济体采取的一系列行动是否构成非法的自由贸易壁垒，目前两大集团距离贸易战又近了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/china-launches-tit-for-tat-investigation-into-eu-trade-barriers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 07:34:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关键政党称泰国大麻政策大转变将损害投资者信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/thai-cannabis-u-turn-to-hurt-investor-confidence-key-party-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国执政联盟第二大党警告称，在历史性大麻合法化仅两年后，泰国就计划将其重新归类为麻醉品，这向外国投资者发出了错误的信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/thai-cannabis-u-turn-to-hurt-investor-confidence-key-party-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 07:09:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>皮尤调查显示美国在数十个国家比中国更受青睐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/us-favored-over-china-in-dozens-of-countries-pew-survey-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皮尤研究中心调查的35个高收入和中等收入国家中，美国的形象远远好于中国，这表明北京在赢得全球人心方面的努力还有很长的路要走。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/us-favored-over-china-in-dozens-of-countries-pew-survey-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 06:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚称接近与新加坡达成经济特区协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/malaysia-says-near-deal-with-singapore-for-special-economic-zone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚称，该国即将与新加坡达成协议，建设东南亚首个跨境经济特区，两国希望该特区能够吸引新的投资并刺激经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/malaysia-says-near-deal-with-singapore-for-special-economic-zone</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 06:02:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称乌克兰可使用英国导弹袭击俄罗斯境内</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/starmer-says-ukraine-can-use-uk-missiles-to-strike-inside-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默暗示乌克兰可以使用英国的“风暴阴影”导弹袭击俄罗斯境内的军事目标，证实他将延续英国上届政府在俄乌战争中使用远程武器的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/starmer-says-ukraine-can-use-uk-missiles-to-strike-inside-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙的前总理寻求中右翼政府协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/macron-s-ex-premier-seeks-center-right-accord-to-form-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的前总理爱德华·菲利普呼吁中间派和中右翼政党联合起来组建新政府，因为在提前选举导致法国议会严重分裂之后，政治角逐愈演愈烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/macron-s-ex-premier-seeks-center-right-accord-to-form-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 19:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国下一届政府将继承韧性增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-next-government-is-set-to-inherit-resilient-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国经济今年预计将保持稳定增长，这将缓解下届政府面临的预算挑战。此前，法国提前大选导致出现悬浮议会，未来财政政策面临巨大不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-next-government-is-set-to-inherit-resilient-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:01:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>到 2030 年，英国可能需要额外 570 亿英镑绿色资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/uk-likely-needs-another-57-billion-for-green-investment-by-2030</link>
      <description><![CDATA[到 2030 年，英国可能需要高达 570 亿英镑（730 亿美元）的额外投资来发展关键产业，新一届工党政府认为这将有助于该国支持绿色就业增长并减少对碳的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/uk-likely-needs-another-57-billion-for-green-investment-by-2030</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 12:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
